{
  "stem": "26983.9",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even we helped without that somebody told it to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We helped to the children from the ghetto Lodz, I think, in--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember Lodz was liquidated in the-- in the late summer, it could be, August, September, something like that, maybe October-- '44, of course.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw all this transport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I even heard the stories from the Sonderkommando-- how they killed the head of the Lodz-- Rumkowski.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was the so-called King of-- of Lodz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The head of the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we saw these children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were in a terrible-- I mean, the children who came into the camp-- again, they came in the Zigeunerlager, in the Gypsy camp-- which, by that time, was not any more a Gypsy camp.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It had only the name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because all the Gypsies were killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were gassed in the beginning of August-- about the 4th of August, '44.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, later on, only few Germans-- the so-called [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Reise ?] Deutschen--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gypsies who had German-- came from German origin, they came, few of them, in our camp, even to the mannerlager, I remember, and later on some of them I met even in Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But all the Gypsies, with the children and mothers, all were gassed about around the 4th of August, '44.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And later on came the other people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like from Lodz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember we helped these children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We collected, between us, soup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And through the electric barbed wire, we were very clever and very, somehow-- we had-- we were very alert.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we pushed through the--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Barbed wire, which was very dangerous-- the soup for the children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on came transport, when they tried to send off all the people from Theresienstadt-- our friend who were still there.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
